channel.description:
[size=18pt][b]FallenPK: A New World Has Just Begun[/b][/size]
FallenPK is a PI server, It is a Pking/Skilling type of server. It has many features like dicing, new shops, and many more! The base of FallenPK is Teamtorva, and I coded all of it, and a help from some tutorials I found in google. FallenPK has 602+ Interfaces, and fixed a lot of bugs in this server, and please comment and tell me what you think :). Also if you need help
Download Package List:

99% Dicing 100% Working Summoning 699+ Interfaces New Bosses New Hitsplats Working Packages Working Clan Chat Working Curses, Ancients & Lunar 602 Shop Interface 602 Anims & Stances & Items
